extendedInfo.description: Free calls to FreePP users or call phones at low rates from your mobile and tablet on the move, as well as sending/receiving SMS and MMS free on Android and iOS. Features: - Make low-cost calls to mobiles and landlines with high-quality sound.- Call from anywhere on the world with the own mobile number displayed. *- Call your friends for free with excellent quality over 2G, 3G, 4G or WiFi. * - Send SMS, images, videos and files to any from contacts.- Group-chat between friends around the world to share lives through texts, voice messages and pictures.- Share the emotion with your own graffiti.  - No user name/password and no need to log in/out: work with your mobile number, and integrates with your existing phone address book. - Never miss messages when your phones are turned off, notifications will arrive when you turn them on.- No advertising.For more information, visit FonePP page: http://fonepp.com.* 2G, 3G, 4G or WiFi required. reviews.title: Johnny Nguyen
reviews.comment: Cheap international VoIP rate! Even cheaper than mobile calling cost in some countries.    Pros:  - very good and clear calling quality with your own mobile number displayed (Caller ID).                 - Can use with 2G (edge).               - Easy to use.               - Pay as you go without hidden charge   Cons:  - required internet connection (2G, 3G, 4G and WiFi).                - Taking about 14 seconds to connect (however better than some other VoIPs and calling cards services)
